HEADWORD: Moule
<hw>Moule</hw> <pr>(m⟦omac⟧l)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>moulen</ets>. See <er>Mold</er>.]</ety> <def>To contract mold; to
grow moldy; to mold.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let us not <qex>moulen</qex> thus in idleness.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

